location: National Cheng Kung University Fall Orchid Show, Taiwan

measurements.description: Three hundred one flowers and 14 buds stunningly displayed on 20 up to 34.4-cm upright inflorescences; plant 24.5 cm wide x 31.4 cm high in a 25-cm diameter plastic pot, media potting soil; dorsal sepal hooded, white, pink marginally, green centrally; lateral sepals white; petals minute, blushed pink; lip trilobed, coral-pink; spur 5.1cm, green proximal half, salmon-pink distal half; substance soft; texture matte; also awarded an AM of 85 points, award 20245401.
